OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry this
OL,6,Fevening with some late sunshine. Then
OL,7,Fthe rest of the night will be dry with
OL,8,Fmostly clear skies but some low cloud
OL,9,Fpossible across the east. Patchy frost.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FDry and mostly sunny
OL,12,Falthough some patchy low cloud may
OL,13,Flinger along the North Sea coast.
OL,14,FWarm, but cooler along the east coast.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,17,Fdry, bright and warm on Friday, chance
OL,18,Fof a few showers. Cooler and and
OL,19,Fcloudier over the weekend with a
OL,20,Fchance of showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
